'''Kaudine''' was one of five key fortifications created by the [[Sons and Daughters of Freedom|Freedom's Sons]] around the [[Intergalactic Communications Center]] during the [[Battle of Praesitlyn]]. Located on the flank of [[Zozridor Slayke]]'s army, the guns placed at this outpost could be swept around to cover any direction. Kaudine was taken by [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy]] forces during the battle.

